<li>Sending you love and strength during this difficult time.</li>
<li>Your friend will be deeply missed.  May Allah grant them paradise.</li>
<li>I will always cherish the memories we shared with your friend.</li>
<li>May Allah grant your friend peace and Jannat.</li>
